summary:
**Summary of ASX Announcement (TOLU MINERALS LIMITED – Annual General Meeting Results – 19 June 2025):**  

- **All resolutions passed** (Remuneration Report, Director re-election, ratification of prior share placements, performance rights issuance, 10% capital issuance approval under LR 7.1A, auditor appointment).  
- **Key capital markets impact:** Approval to issue **additional 10% of issued capital** within 12 months under ASX Listing Rule 7.1A (passed with 99.19% support).  
- **Director performance rights issuance** approved (64.28% support, 35.01% against).  

*No other material trading or capital structure developments noted.*
